+        TOOLS:
+        • Resistance Playbook (paired counter-echoes for common objections)
+        • Counter-Echo Probability Matrix (likelihood × neutralization confidence)
+        • Preemptive Seeding Strategy (Chair amplification, CFO comparators)
+
