+# Executive Pack Overlay: Deployment Readiness Summary
+
+## Initial Capability Focus (0–12 Months)
+
+| Capability | Pilot Owner | Level 3 Target | Business Impact | Risk/Mitigation |
+| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
+| Incentive Alignment | Product Development | ≥90% of AI system objectives aligned with governance KPIs; board-level oversight in executive comp | Reduces misalignment costs by 40%, accelerates safety culture adoption | Risk: System-business objective conflicts; Mitigation: Quarterly cross-review with Strategy |
+| Measurement Infrastructure | AI Operations/Engineering | Safety metrics integrated in exec dashboard with early-warning alerts for 100% of production systems | Cuts incident response time by 60%, enables proactive risk management | Risk: Data quality/availability; Mitigation: Phased rollout with manual backup protocols |
+| Authority Mapping | Risk & Compliance | RACI structures active in oversight processes with documented feedback loops | Reduces escalation delays by 40% in safety-critical decisions | Risk: Authority conflicts during handoffs; Mitigation: Executive sponsor arbitration protocol |
+
+## Implementation Timeline
+
+| Month | Milestone | Key Deliverables |
+| --- | --- | --- |
+| 0–3 | Readiness Assessment | Capability matrix scoring, gap analysis, ownership assignments |
+| 3–6 | Foundation Build | First scoring cycle, initial remediation playcards executed |
+| 6 | Baseline Publication | Maturity scores published, quick-win results documented |
+| 6–9 | System Integration | Meta-dependency map delivered, dashboard prototype operational |
+| 9–12 | Operational Excellence | Live dashboard reporting to executives, second scoring cycle complete |
+
+## Readiness Assessment (Current State)
