+| Product Development | 🟡 Amber | Strong system knowledge, needs governance process integration |
+| AI Operations | 🟢 Green | Technical capabilities established, measurement protocols ready |
+| Risk & Compliance | 🟡 Amber | Governance experience strong, needs AI-specific adaptation |
