+## Decision Points Linked to Deliverables
+
+- Month 6: Meta-dependency map informs FY26 budget allocation for governance capability build-out
+- Month 9: Dashboard prototype results determine enterprise-wide rollout strategy
+- Month 12: Second scoring cycle validates investment case for advanced governance capabilities
+
